{"tid":1186740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[移民]大家心目中嘅理想國係...","createTime":"2019-06-05T06:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T03:55:14.000Z","uid":126320,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bcd1b22fb961c1f5acdd6c119c9593329b1a2b7d","tid":1186740,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"1. 台灣,日本,韓國<br />\n  <br />\n好處:<br />\n大家都屬於東亞文化圈容易溝通, 練好當地語言嘅話, 仲可以偽裝成為地道當地人, 因為樣貌同膚色都好相似,一樣過農曆新年, 儒家文化 , 比較容易適應,唔會咁歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壞處: 當地人一開頭會視我哋為支國人, 因為佢哋唔太識分, 個朵畀人搞臭咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.西方國家, 例如:美英澳紐德法,等...<br />\n<br />\n好處:<br />\n同支國喺敵對,人生安全較高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壞處:<br />\n種族歧視, 文化太多元, 伊斯蘭教,恐怖襲擊, 白人主義, 左膠主義, 難民當道, 融入難道高等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下影片為歐洲被伊斯蘭化的例子:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WMq48VTRp7U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWMq48VTRp7U&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=cf8ff047\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WMq48VTRp7U</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.非州國家<br />\n<br />\n好處: <br />\n移居當地立即成為當地富豪, 要咩有咩,  利用&ldquo;中國人&rdquo;身分 ,立即成為特權階層,與狼同行。<br />\n而且山高皇帝遠又唔使受到支國箝制, 反而可以呢個身份.........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 娶廿幾三十個非洲老婆都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壞處: <br />\n基礎建設極差,疾病橫行,單火橫行,一朝喪命。黑人男女通吃, 萬能插蘇,社會極不平等, 就算畀你有十間豪華獨立屋都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有隨時比人勒索同打家劫舍 。<br />\n喺街度畀人強制中出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔請食蕉都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n大家嘅理想國又係咩呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要具備咩元素?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n移民又會去邊度?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎交流討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3ac10366240346db34d57ec897686f979b29c5","tid":1186740,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bcd1b22fb961c1f5acdd6c119c9593329b1a2b7d","tid":1186740,"uid":126320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"1. 台灣,日本,韓國<br />\n  <br />\n好處:<br />\n大家都屬於東亞文化圈容易溝通, 練好當地語言嘅話, 仲可以偽裝成為地道當地人, 因為樣貌同膚色都好相似,一樣過農曆新年, 儒家文化 , 比較容易適應,唔會咁歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壞處: 當地人一開頭會視我哋為支國人, 因為佢哋唔太識分, 個朵畀人搞臭咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.西方國家, 例如:美英澳紐德法,等...<br />\n<br />\n好處:<br />\n同支國喺敵對,人生安全較高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壞處:<br />\n種族歧視, 文化太多元, 伊斯蘭教,恐怖襲擊, 白人主義, 左膠主義, 難民